Subject: External Storage: Shadowing + System Backup inconsistent    [ ref:!00D70091pB.!500Qk0IcDl4:ref ]

TextBody:
Hello,

1. "File not found" is usually appears when the shadow is not yet uploaded to the server. In this case, you can check the computer under C:WindowsSystem32configsystemprofileAppDataLocalCoSoSysEPPshadows.
We can schedule a remote connection to generate a shadow and check the transfer from the backend.

2. I am not sure Backup V2 is included in the external storage.

Kind regards
__________________
Andrei Pop | Technical Support Engineer
Netwrix Endpoint Protector
